  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went back to Warsaw after two or three years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the most was they make the-- they want to make them orderly, collect the soldiers to put them on the-- on the-- on the-- on the highway.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Right It was huge from both sides.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they keep them [INAUDIBLE] and the-- the German Luftwaffe bombard it, and makes a mess, really.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not most, but many.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know because you never know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, there was many killed, but you see killed soldiers, but you don't know how many.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you see killed soldiers, horses, and everything mixed up the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got back to Warsaw, they start, again, organize the soldiers to keep some [POLISH], as the call to protect Warsaw from the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was in the Warsaw squadron.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was close to what they call [POLISH] applies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- we-- we sit there and-- with a few rifles.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we want to-- to-- to stops them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you know, the houses in-- in-- in-- in-- in [INAUDIBLE] but the houses are not compact together, but different houses.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they live under the houses to-- to have some protection and shoot them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and-- in a few nights, we attacked, but they-- they-- they-- they have prepared items, have prepared the [NON-ENGLISH] what they call the special weapons.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they shoot, and they-- and they-- and they-- and they shoot out, and the shrapnel, they fell after the houses.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was-- yes, but, so they have to give up, and-- and they take us to-- to leave-- the-- the rifles, to leave everything.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they put in different places, and leave everything and go home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I got home, I say we were going to run from the place.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
